Class ComboBoxBuilder<T>

java.lang.Object
org.panteleyev.fx.combobox.ComboBoxBuilder<T>
Type Parameters:
T - type of the ComboBox items
public class ComboBoxBuilder<T> extends Object
This class implements builder that creates instances of ComboBox. Builder configuration is done using user defined consumer. Example:
